ZH: 我们每个人都有言论自由的权利。
EN: We all have the right to freedom of speech.
ZH: 她坚持自己的权利，不愿让步。
EN: She insisted on her rights and refused to compromise.
ZH: 这是每个人的基本权利。
EN: This is a fundamental right of every person.
ZH: 法律赋予我们许多权利和义务。
EN: The law gives us many rights and responsibilities.
ZH: 他努力争取自己的权利。
EN: He fought hard for his rights.
ZH: 她认为自己被剥夺了基本的权利。
EN: She felt that her basic rights had been violated.
ZH: 他知道自己有权利反抗不公正的待遇。
EN: He knew he had the right to resist unfair treatment.
ZH: 在这个国家，每个人都有平等的权利。
EN: In this country, everyone has equal rights.
ZH: 宪法保障了公民的权利。
EN: The constitution guarantees the rights of citizens.
ZH: 我们不应该忽视他人的权利和感受。
EN: We should not disregard the rights and feelings of others.
ZH: 这个法律保护了儿童的权利。
EN: This law protects the rights of children.
ZH: 他们为保护环境权利而奋斗。
EN: They are fighting to protect the rights of the environment.
ZH: 请尊重他人的隐私权利。
EN: Please respect the privacy rights of others.
ZH: 公司的职员有权利在需要时请假。
EN: Employees of the company have the right to take days off when needed.
ZH: 我们要维护人民的合法权利。
EN: We must defend the legitimate rights of the people.
ZH: 他们不服从法庭的裁决，宣称自己拥有更高的权利。
EN: They refused to comply with the court's ruling, claiming they had higher rights.
ZH: 每个人都应该被尊重和平等对待，因为这是基本的权利。
EN: Everyone should be respected and treated equally, as it is a fundamental right.
ZH: 被告有权利获得辩护律师。
EN: The defendant has the right to an attorney.
ZH: 公民有权利参与政府的决策过程。
EN: Citizens have the right to take part in the government's decision-making process.
